name: Frederik Mikkelsen
body:
### Welcome
My name is Frederik Mikkelsen and I'm a Danish student who goes by the name Frederikam or Fre_d. Despite having no formal education about software development, I still manage to produce various pieces of software.

### Things I've built:
* [FredBoat](https://github.com/Frederikam/FredBoat) a Discord bot.
* [FredBoatMusic](https://github.com/Frederikam/FredBoatMusic) a music bot for Discord.
* [Screeps Script Downloader](https://github.com/Frederikam/Screeps-Script-Downloader) download your Screeps script instead of copy-pasting them.
* [My Screeps scripts](https://github.com/Frederikam/Screeps)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
